# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s05_f12f7a0c:

    # "Most people imagine Indian reservations as tucked away slices of heaven. Maybe some pocketed oasis of vibrant greens and flowing water in what is otherwise a wasteland."
    "La mayoría de la gente imagina las reservaciones indígenas como pedazos escondidos del paraíso. Tal vez algún oasis escondido de verdes vibrantes y agua fluyente en lo que de otro modo sería un yermo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s05_fef2a789:

    # "Those people are wrong."
    "Esa gente está equivocada."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s05_194086bc:

    # "The Navajo reservation is as sandy and barren as the rest of the desert, and at 22,475 miles, it’s neither green nor funsized."
    "La reservación Navajo es tan arenosa y árida como el resto del desierto, y con 22,475 millas, no es ni verde ni de tamaño divertido."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s05_37da4d4d:

    # "Not that I hate it."
    "No es que lo odie."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s05_4fe75e53:

    # "The miles of faded highway road whooshes by, blending together with the sand that stretches out to far off, rigid mountain."
    "Las millas de carretera descolorida pasan zumbando, fusionándose con la arena que se extiende hasta montañas rígidas y lejanas."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:57
translate spanish hwb_s05_f3e0378e:

    # "Like there’s a rhythm to it all."
    "Como si hubiera un ritmo en todo ello."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:59
translate spanish hwb_s05_c0f1d602:

    # "Behind me, Marina is still stretched out on the fold out bed, cuddling the pillow, a substitute for her blanket that’s long since fallen off her bed."
    "Detrás de mí, Marina sigue estirada en la cama plegable, abrazando la almohada, un sustituto de su manta que hace tiempo se cayó de su cama."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s05_842e9c55:

    # "My old gym clothes are a little small for her, the shorts only reaching halfway down her thighs."
    "Mi vieja ropa de gimnasio le queda un poco pequeña, los shorts solo le llegan a la mitad de los muslos."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s05_4cc69cda:

    # "But hey, I’m not complaining."
    "Pero oye, no me quejo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:65
translate spanish hwb_s05_2e78a243:

    # "Soon we’re rolling into the town, its jagged namesake peeking over the horizon—Shiprock."
    "Pronto llegamos al pueblo, su nombre irregular asomándose sobre el horizonte: Shiprock."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s05_465691e4:

    # "The town itself is typical for this desert. Nothing fancy like a highrise. Just a whole lot of plain shacks sitting on top of gravel, painted worn browns and beiges."
    "El pueblo en sí es típico de este desierto. Nada lujoso como un rascacielos. Solo un montón de chozas simples sobre grava, pintadas de marrones y beiges desgastados."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:69
translate spanish hwb_s05_4c0cf8ac:

    # "From behind me, there's a light, almost fluffy yawn."
    "Desde detrás de mí, hay un bostezo ligero, casi esponjoso."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s05_04dc7a82:

    # "I wonder how that bundle of joy handles mornings."
    "Me pregunto cómo maneja las mañanas ese manojo de alegría."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:114
translate spanish hwb_s05_9cde120a:

    # Marina "Morning…"
    Marina "Доброе утро..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:116
translate spanish hwb_s05_06c8f012:

    # Amber "Oh hey, you’re finally awake."
    Amber "О, привет, ты наконец проснулась."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:118
translate spanish hwb_s05_84605f97:

    # Marina "Uh-huh…"
    Marina "Угу..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:124
translate spanish hwb_s05_4096eac4:

    # "She yawns again and thumps back against the bed."
    "Vuelve a bostezar y se deja caer de golpe contra la cama."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:126
translate spanish hwb_s05_02eec46b:

    # "Guess she’s not a morning person."
    "Supongo que no es una persona mañanera."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s05_883ae5bb:

    # Amber "There’s still some coffee in th-"
    Amber "Тут осталось немного кофе в-"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s05_65a1fb69:

    # Marina "{size=+10}OH WOW IS THAT SHIPROCK!{/size}" with hpunch
    Marina "{size=+10}ОЙ-ЙОЙ НЕУЖЕЛИ ЭТО ШИПРОК!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s05_f5fd2c5b:

    # "I take it back."
    "Retiro lo dicho."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:160
translate spanish hwb_s05_29988951:

    # "Marina rushes behind me and grabs the back of the seats, her eyes sparkling."
    "Marina corre detrás de mí y agarra la parte trasera de los asientos, con los ojos brillando."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:162
translate spanish hwb_s05_b4d49a2c:

    # Marina "It’s huge! I can’t believe we can see it from so far away!"
    Marina "Она огромная! Не могу поверить, что ее видно даже отсюда!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:164
translate spanish hwb_s05_0f41d15e:

    # "On closer inspection, my clothes are {i}way{/i} too tight for her. My poor shirt is being stretched to its limit."
    "Al mirar más de cerca, mi ropa le queda {i}demasiado{/i} apretada. Mi pobre camiseta está siendo estirada al límite."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:168
translate spanish hwb_s05_cf11f40d:

    # "Of course, this doesn’t seem to bother her at all."
    "Por supuesto, esto no parece molestarla en absoluto."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:172
translate spanish hwb_s05_c8548fbf:

    # "I don’t know if I’m more embarrassed for myself or for her."
    "No sé si estoy más avergonzada por mí o por ella."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:178
translate spanish hwb_s05_bf17e4bc:

    # Amber "W-{w=0.3}Well, we have to get moving now, so go get dressed or whatever."
    Amber "Н-нам надо двигаться дальше, так что оденься что ли."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:182
translate spanish hwb_s05_99a0f1da:

    # Marina "Ah, sure thing."
    Marina "Ах, конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s05_08769514:

    # "She scampers off to the back, finally giving me room to breathe as I make my way to the driver's seat…"
    "Sale corriendo hacia la parte de atrás, por fin dándome espacio para respirar mientras me dirijo al asiento del conductor..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s05_9bafe57e:

    # "Until I accidentally glance at the rearview mirror."
    "Hasta que accidentalmente miro el espejo retrovisor."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s05_9c8c2031:

    # "In the middle of the motorhome, Marina slips out of her pajamas and into her regular clothes."
    "En medio de la casa rodante, Marina se quita el pijama y se pone su ropa normal."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:203
translate spanish hwb_s05_416d376c:

    # "Geez, the bathroom is right there."
    "Caray, el baño está justo ahí."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:207
translate spanish hwb_s05_0b202830:

    # "I adjust the mirror and try my hardest to stay focused on anything else I can look at."
    "Ajusto el espejo y hago todo lo posible por concentrarme en cualquier otra cosa que pueda mirar."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s05_9bed1293:

    # "Fully dressed, Marina pops back up beside me and settles in the passenger’s seat."
    "Ya vestida, Marina aparece de nuevo a mi lado y se acomoda en el asiento del pasajero."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:252
translate spanish hwb_s05_787dbd47:

    # "The desolate road continues until suddenly, as if out of nowhere, we’re greeted by a line of cars, RVs, buses, and every other kind of vehicle under this blazing sun. All lumped together, stacked one on top of the other, side by side, and every single one blasting their horns."
    "El camino desolado continúa hasta que, de repente, como si salieran de la nada, nos recibe una fila de autos, casas rodantes, autobuses y todo tipo de vehículo bajo este sol abrasador. Todos amontonados, apilados uno sobre otro, lado a lado, y cada uno tocando la bocina sin parar."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:260
translate spanish hwb_s05_5bb27f16:

    # Amber "What the…"
    Amber "Что за..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:264
translate spanish hwb_s05_1276b856:

    # Marina "Whoa, you think this is because of the treasure?"
    Marina "Нифига ж себе! Ты думаешь это из-за сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:268
translate spanish hwb_s05_d0a5d697:

    # "I grit my teeth and flop back in my seat."
    "Aprieto los dientes y me dejo caer en mi asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:270
translate spanish hwb_s05_5c1b0751:

    # "I can only pray these are tourists, and I was the only one dumb enough to humor this scam."
    "Solo puedo rezar para que sean turistas, y que yo sea la única lo suficientemente tonta como para caer en esta estafa."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:274
translate spanish hwb_s05_3f73bdde:

    # "We’re soon assimilated into the traffic jam. Slowly, the motorhome inches forward. But when we finally reach the front, a whole new monster awaits us."
    "Pronto somos absorbidos por el embotellamiento. Lentamente, la casa rodante avanza centímetro a centímetro. Pero cuando finalmente llegamos al frente, un monstruo completamente nuevo nos espera."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:276
translate spanish hwb_s05_763f3355:

    # "Laid out on the dirt, barely in the shadow of the looming mountain, is a giant cluster that can only be described as such."
    "Extendido sobre la tierra, apenas a la sombra de la imponente montaña, hay un conglomerado gigante que solo puede describirse así."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:278
translate spanish hwb_s05_a26513ba:

    # "Campers, tents, tarps, booths—you name it."
    "Campistas, tiendas de campaña, lonas, puestos—lo que te imagines."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:280
translate spanish hwb_s05_0ffe3157:

    # "A chaotic hoard of people crowd around the entire unorganized mess."
    "Una caótica multitud de personas se aglomera alrededor de todo ese desorden."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s05_be072e67:

    # "I cringe at the very sight of it."
    "Me estremezco con solo verlo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:284
translate spanish hwb_s05_c8a6f392:

    # "I’m in hell."
    "Estoy en el infierno."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:286
translate spanish hwb_s05_3d93979b:

    # "Marina pushes her face against the window, in awe of the sheer insanity."
    "Marina aprieta su rostro contra la ventana, asombrada por la pura locura."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:290
translate spanish hwb_s05_7017e187:

    # Marina "I-I don’t think I’ve seen this many people since the concert."
    Marina "Я не видела так много людей с тех пор как была на концерте."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:292
translate spanish hwb_s05_6b4969ad:

    # "Oh god, she’s going to break from the over-stimulation."
    "Oh dios, va a colapsar por la sobreestimulación."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:294
translate spanish hwb_s05_15fa05b9:

    # "A choir of horns serenade us from behind. Groaning, I pull forward and squeeze the motorhome into the nearest available space, stuffed tightly between everything else."
    "Un coro de bocinas nos serenata desde atrás. Gimiendo, avanzo y meto la casa rodante en el espacio más cercano disponible, apretujada entre todo lo demás."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:296
translate spanish hwb_s05_74700ac8:

    # "Backing out is gonna be a real pain."
    "Salir marcha atrás va a ser un verdadero dolor de cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s05_04e63eb1:

    # Marina "Well, what are we waiting for? Let’s go find that treasure!"
    Marina "Отлично, чего же мы ждем? Пойдем искать сокровище!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s05_e46f34a2:

    # "Marina sits up and nearly leaps out of the car, but I grab her wrist and pull her back into her seat."
    "Marina se endereza y casi salta del auto, pero la agarro de la muñeca y la regreso a su asiento."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:306
translate spanish hwb_s05_1b7fc4c1:

    # Amber "Just hold on a second."
    Amber "Подожди секунду."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s05_c09151df:

    # "Her enthusiasm fades."
    "Su entusiasmo se desvanece."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s05_5f5cda5d:

    # Marina "Oh, that’s right. You were only going to drop me off and leave."
    Marina "Ох, точно. Ты же только высаживаешь меня и уезжаешь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s05_709a7b88:

    # Amber "Sorry, but I’m gonna stick around a bit longer."
    Amber "Извини, но я собираюсь ненадолго задержаться."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s05_0e18d299:

    # Marina "F-For real?"
    Marina "П-правда?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s05_63acb99c:

    # "She starts sniffling."
    "Empieza a sollozar."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s05_77678e69:

    # Marina "You’re so nice to me, Amber. I-I think I might cry."
    Marina "Ты так добра ко мне Эмбер. Я-я, мне кажется что я сейчас заплачу."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:324
translate spanish hwb_s05_71df12cd:

    # Amber "Hold it in. We gotta think of a game plan first."
    Amber "Терпи. Сперва мы должны обдумать план игры."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:328
translate spanish hwb_s05_8eb58b3b:

    # Marina "‘Kay."
    Marina "Ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s05_b622185b:

    # "Marina returns to her usual happy-go-lucky self while I grimace at the chaos outside."
    "Marina vuelve a su habitual yo alegre y despreocupada mientras yo hago una mueca ante el caos afuera."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s05_ccf3d396:

    # "If I suspend my disbelief and assume the treasure is real, where would we even start?"
    "Si suspendo mi incredulidad y asumo que el tesoro es real, ¿por dónde empezaríamos siquiera?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s05_7ac4528a:

    # "We don’t even have any equipment."
    "Ni siquiera tenemos equipo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s05_0d92b615:

    # Amber "I guess we may as well start by checking out the place."
    Amber "Я полагаю, мы должны начать осматривать это место."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:378
translate spanish hwb_s05_30d45690:

    # "I'm the first to make my way out into the sea of people. My nose is assaulted with smells of campfires and B.O. masked in suntan lotion."
    "Soy la primera en abrirme paso entre el mar de gente. Mi nariz es asaltada por olores a fogatas y a B.O. disimulado con bloqueador solar."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:383
translate spanish hwb_s05_ce8451ec:

    # "Smells like tourist alright."
    "Huele a turista, sin duda."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s05_5c8ecbad:

    # "Marina finishes her run around the motorhome and huddles close to me, her eyes still wide with wonder, but far less gung ho than before."
    "Marina termina su carrera alrededor de la casa rodante y se acurruca cerca de mí, sus ojos aún llenos de asombro, pero mucho menos entusiasta que antes."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:397
translate spanish hwb_s05_57c4c6e5:

    # "The two of us make our way through the makeshift campground, following a guardrail that’s been set up to separate the visitors from the rock."
    "Las dos nos abrimos paso por el campamento improvisado, siguiendo una barandilla que han puesto para separar a los visitantes de la roca."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s05_034ed451:

    # "All the while, we pass different scenes starring all sorts of people: A news anchor elbowing nosey hecklers out of the way while she tries to report, men on top of motorhomes in lawn chairs, strumming away on guitars."
    "Mientras tanto, pasamos junto a diferentes escenas protagonizadas por todo tipo de personas: una presentadora de noticias apartando a mirones entrometidos con los codos mientras intenta reportar, hombres encima de casas rodantes en sillas de jardín, rasgueando guitarras."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:401
translate spanish hwb_s05_a8173597:

    # "Even vendors have set up shop here, selling over-ripened fruit from their booths."
    "Hasta vendedores ambulantes han montado sus puestos aquí, vendiendo fruta demasiado madura desde sus casetas."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:403
translate spanish hwb_s05_e4e0d3fa:

    # "Marina is speechless, looking on in overwhelmed curiosity and hovering so close I keep tripping over her. I’m half expecting her to grab onto one of my belt loops."
    "Marina está sin palabras, mirando con una curiosidad abrumada y tan pegada a mí que no dejo de tropezarme con ella. Medio espero que se agarre de uno de mis pasadores del cinturón."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:405
translate spanish hwb_s05_0bb49ca3:

    # "I’m surprised. I pegged her to be pretty good with crowds."
    "Estoy sorprendida. La había catalogado como alguien bastante buena con las multitudes."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:410
translate spanish strings:
    old "Man"
    new "Мужчина"
translate spanish hwb_s05_f09e358b:

    # "Man" "{size=+10}PLEASE STAY BEHIND THE GUARDRAIL! I REPEAT, {w=0.4}PLEASE STAY BEHIND THE GUARDRAIL!{/size}" with hpunch
    Man "{size=+10}ПОЖАЛУЙСТА, ОСТАВАЙТЕСЬ ЗА ОГРАЖДЕНИЕМ! Я ПОВТОРЯЮ, {w=0.4}ПОЖАЛУЙСТА, ОСТАВАЙТЕСЬ ЗА ОГРАЖДЕНИЕМ!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s05_02065221:

    # "A booming voice shouts over the crackling of a megaphone. Pushing through the crowd, we’re shoved into a part of the crowd that’s mobbing by an opening in the guardrail."
    "Una voz retumbante grita por encima del crujido de un megáfono. Abriéndonos paso entre la multitud, nos empujan hacia una parte de la gente que se agolpa junto a una abertura en la barandilla."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s05_02aa8956:

    # "They’re barred from advancing by a lone man, standing on top of a folding chair and clutching his megaphone like a shotgun."
    "Están impedidos de avanzar por un hombre solitario, de pie sobre una silla plegable y agarrando su megáfono como si fuera una escopeta."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s05_f714fb67:

    # "Man" "{size=+10}STAY BEHIND THE GUARDRAIL! PLEASE BE CONSIDERATE OF NAVAJO LAND!{/size}"
    Man "{size=+10}ОСТАВАЙТЕСЬ ЗА ОГРАЖДЕНИЕМ! ПОЖАЛУЙСТА, УВАЖАЙТЕ ЗЕМЛИ НАВАХО!{/size}"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s05_8e9285f1:

    # Marina "What’s going on?"
    Marina "Что происходит?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s05_84b0a74d:

    # Amber "Not sure."
    Amber "Без понятия."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s05_42d8c9ff:

    # Amber "I think…"
    Amber "Кажется..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s05_636314c6:

    # "The sun reflects off of the truck behind it. I squint my eyes at the word printed on its side."
    "El sol se refleja en la camioneta detrás de él. Entrecierro los ojos ante la palabra impresa en su costado."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s05_7b8e192d:

    # "\"Navajo Parks and Recreation\""
    "\"Parques y Recreación Navajo\""

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s05_70c2d338:

    # Amber "It’s the Man?"
    Amber "Этот тут главный?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s05_492f511c:

    # Marina "The Man?"
    Marina "Главный?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s05_2f38302a:

    # Amber "Uh, nevermind."
    Amber "Ох, забудь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s05_d51595ea:

    # "The relentless crowd ignores him, ramming into each other as they fling whole dictionaries' worth of profanity at him."
    "La multitud implacable lo ignora, chocando entre sí mientras le lanzan diccionarios enteros de insultos."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s05_10f5f612:

    # Amber "This could get nasty."
    Amber "Это может выйти из-под контроля."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s05_e9add82a:

    # Marina "Maybe they’re moshing? People did that at the concert."
    Marina "Может они слэмятся? Я видела такое на концерте."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s05_458031c8:

    # Amber "Just what the hell kind of concert did you go to anyw—"
    Amber "Что за концерты такие, черт поде -"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s05_5b6a7400:

    # Amber "Wait a second."
    Amber "Погоди-ка."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s05_cf0f2089:

    # "In the back of the ‘mosh,’ distant from the calamity, is a familiar sight: Blonde hair, intertwined and running through a dark red bandanna."
    "Al fondo del 'pogo', lejos del caos, hay una vista familiar: Cabello rubio, entrelazado y corriendo a través de un pañuelo rojo oscuro."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:470
translate spanish hwb_s05_55fac5ba:

    # Marina "What’s wrong?"
    Marina "Что такое?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s05_9fcfe0e9:

    # Amber "Remember that loud chick from the gas station?"
    Amber "Помнишь ту шумную девку с заправки?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s05_d24c7658:

    # Marina "A little. I was too busy with my slushie to really notice."
    Marina "Немного. Я была слишком занята коктейлем, не обратила внимания."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:482
translate spanish hwb_s05_cbb21f84:

    # Marina "Why?"
    Marina "Почему ты спросила?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s05_f2a33a74:

    # Amber "I think we just found our first lead."
    Amber "Я думаю, что мы нашли первую зацепку."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s05_5c35fb0e:

    # "My voice trails off and I start towards the girl, pushing my way through the crowd."
    "Mi voz se apaga y me dirijo hacia la chica, abriéndome paso entre la multitud."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s05_4e757171:

    # Marina "Hey, Amber, wait!"
    Marina "Эй, Эмбер, подожди!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:505
translate spanish hwb_s05_58c7c8e1:

    # "Putting on my person mask, I take a breath and place my hand on her shoulder with a forced smile."
    "Poniéndome mi máscara personal, respiro hondo y coloco mi mano en su hombro con una sonrisa forzada."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:519
translate spanish hwb_s05_a61c8fbe:

    # BandanaGirl "For the last time, old man, I don’t have any!"
    BandanaGirl "Последний раз говорю, старик, у меня ничего нет!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:524
translate spanish hwb_s05_1220824c:

    # Amber "Huh?"
    Amber "Чего?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s05_1c02c8e0:

    # "She whips around, her eyes prepared for murder, but her features switch to standby mode as she realizes her mistake."
    "Se da la vuelta de golpe, sus ojos preparados para matar, pero sus rasgos cambian a modo de espera al darse cuenta de su error."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s05_a983bc07:

    # BandanaGirl "Oh."
    BandanaGirl "Ой."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:534
translate spanish hwb_s05_dd47e3c5:

    # Amber "Uh, sorry, but didn't I see you at that convenience store yesterday?"
    Amber "Извини, но не тебя ли я видела в магазине вчера?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s05_90a9d9e6:

    # BandanaGirl "Oh yeah, that dump. Outside of Roswell, right?"
    BandanaGirl "Ах да, в той дыре. За Розуэллом, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:542
translate spanish hwb_s05_839d0568:

    # Amber "Yep. That was us. I’m Amber. The other girl is Marina."
    Amber "Да. Это были мы. Я Эмбер. А это Марина."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:548
translate spanish hwb_s05_dc0cfcdb:

    # "Marina waves and I extend my hand. The girl’s eyes narrow, but she eventually shakes it with a surprisingly strong grip."
    "Marina saluda y yo extiendo mi mano. La chica entrecierra los ojos, pero finalmente la estrecha con un agarre sorprendentemente fuerte."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:550
translate spanish hwb_s05_d1a92c5e:

    # Mariah "Mariah."
    Mariah "Мария."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:554
translate spanish hwb_s05_928efc62:

    # Amber "Everyone here for the treasure?"
    Amber "Все здесь ради сокровища?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:558
translate spanish hwb_s05_bb3bb1d8:

    # Mariah "They'd be idiots if they weren't."
    Mariah "В ином случае они были бы полными кретинами."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s05_6e9acd4a:

    # Marina "Hey, what do you know? You were right, Amber!"
    Marina "Эй, смотри-ка! Ты была права, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s05_8ddc9e92:

    # Amber "You say that like it's a good thing."
    Amber "И ничего хорошего в этом нет."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:571
translate spanish hwb_s05_765aa98c:

    # Mariah "You guys here for the gold, too? Not sure why else somebody would come out…"
    Mariah "Вы здесь тоже за золотом? Надо думать, иначе зачем кому-то тащиться..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:573
translate spanish hwb_s05_de9f3ace:

    # "She looks over the scenery and wrinkles her nose."
    "Observa el paisaje y arruga la nariz."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:577
translate spanish hwb_s05_dc5e5ff1:

    # Mariah "…to this place."
    Mariah "...сюда."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:579
translate spanish hwb_s05_700a334d:

    # Amber "The ray of sunshine next to me is looking for the gold. I'm just the ride."
    Amber "Вот это солнышко рядом со мной ищет золото. А я просто катаюсь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:586
translate spanish hwb_s05_c4ce7f00:

    # "Man" "{size=+10}STEP AWAY FROM THE GUARDRAIL! {w=0.5}YOU'RE ALL GETTING OUT OF HAND!{/size}" with hpunch
    Man "{size=+10}ОТОЙДИТЕ ОТ ПЕРИЛ! {w=0.5}НЕМЕДЛЕННО!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:588
translate spanish hwb_s05_441384b8:

    # "The hoard presses in, the yelling grows louder."
    "La horda aprieta, los gritos se vuelven más fuertes."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:590
translate spanish hwb_s05_6bd87f28:

    # "Man" "YOU AREN’T GETTING THROUGH, SO I DON’T EVEN KNOW WHY—"
    Man "ВЫ НЕ ПРОЙДЕТЕ, ПОЭТОМУ Я ДАЖЕ НЕ ЗНАЮ, ЗАЧЕМ—"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:592
translate spanish hwb_s05_98b037cb:

    # "A can of beer flies through the air and cracks him on the forehead, the liquid running down his face."
    "Una lata de cerveza vuela por el aire y le golpea en la frente, el líquido corriéndole por la cara."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:594
translate spanish hwb_s05_eba7146d:

    # "Man" "OH COME ON!"
    Man "ОЙ, ДА ЛАДНО!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:598
translate spanish hwb_s05_f29afc8d:

    # Amber "Um…"
    Amber "Хм..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:604
translate spanish hwb_s05_ca27b22a:

    # Mariah "Navajo Parks and Recreation. They’re trying to keep well-meaning treasure hunters from carving up the rock because of its \"religious significance.\""
    Mariah "Парки и Зоны отдыха Навахо. Они пытаются защитить гору от охотников за сокровищами из-за ее “религиозного значения”."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:608
translate spanish hwb_s05_df823293:

    # Amber "Doesn’t surprise me. This is a Four Corners state, so there’s lots of stuff like that out here."
    Amber "Не удивительно. Это же регион Четырех Углов, тут много таких вещей."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:612
translate spanish hwb_s05_47e9888f:

    # Marina "I think it’s sweet that they’re trying to protect big ol’ Shippy."
    Marina "Мне кажется,  это мило, пытаться защитить Старину Шиппи."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:614
translate spanish hwb_s05_8a9361ed:

    # "Mariah stares at her, as if questioning her entire existence."
    "Mariah la mira fijamente, como cuestionando su propia existencia."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:618
translate spanish hwb_s05_86061028:

    # Mariah "But it’s a rock."
    Mariah "Но это скала."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:622
translate spanish hwb_s05_1e67bd3f:

    # Marina "So?"
    Marina "И?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:626
translate spanish hwb_s05_63d5ba80:

    # Mariah "It’s only good for postcards and carving big monuments. Why's it such a big deal if people want to look for the treasure up there?"
    Mariah "Она годится только для открыток и высекания монументов. Что с того, если люди хотят поискать там сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:630
translate spanish hwb_s05_360cce97:

    # Amber "Well, it’s not gonna make much of a difference either way."
    Amber "Все равно никакого смысла в этом нет."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:634
translate spanish hwb_s05_4ccf1a5d:

    # Mariah "Why’s that? You a non-believer?"
    Mariah "Почему это? Ты не веришь?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:638
translate spanish hwb_s05_987d177d:

    # Amber "No, I’m just not a sucker."
    Amber "Нет, мне же не пять лет."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:642
translate spanish hwb_s05_8e8e602f:

    # Marina "That’s not very nice, Amber."
    Marina "Это некрасиво, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:646
translate spanish hwb_s05_ae8a1982:

    # Amber "Well it’s true."
    Amber "Зато правда."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:650
translate spanish hwb_s05_b75bf55c:

    # Amber "It’s obvious that this is all just an elaborate scam and everyone got ripped off."
    Amber "Ясно же, что это продуманная схема и всех просто развели на деньги."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:652
translate spanish hwb_s05_e4ab615a:

    # "Before I’ve finished my sentence, a cocky, overgrown smile makes its way onto Mariah’s face, oozing with snide confidence."
    "Antes de que termine mi frase, una sonrisa arrogante y desmedida se dibuja en el rostro de Mariah, rebosante de confianza sarcástica."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:656
translate spanish hwb_s05_6ca7ea66:

    # Mariah "What if I told you I could prove the treasure is real?"
    Mariah "А если б я доказала тебе, что сокровище существует?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:660
translate spanish hwb_s05_8288841f:

    # Amber "I’d say you’re full of it."
    Amber "Я бы сказала, что ты брешешь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:664
translate spanish hwb_s05_c27c8695:

    # Marina "Does that mean the treasure is real? Like, honest to goodness real?"
    Marina "Это значит, что сокровище реально? Без шуточек реально?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:679
translate spanish hwb_s05_d7b7484f:

    # "Overwhelmed with excitement, Marina springs up and down, all while Mariah gives a smug nod."
    "Abrumada por la emoción, Marina brinca de arriba abajo, mientras Mariah asiente con suficiencia."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:681
translate spanish hwb_s05_f64d365d:

    # Mariah "{cps=15}Mhm.{/cps}"
    Mariah "{cps=15}Угу.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:685
translate spanish hwb_s05_8e6379a5:

    # Amber "Yeah right."
    Amber "Ага, конечно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:689
translate spanish hwb_s05_83b31eea:

    # Mariah "Oh ye of little faith. I said I could prove it, didn’t I?"
    Mariah "Можешь не верить. Я ведь сказала, что докажу, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:693
translate spanish hwb_s05_43d68e62:

    # Amber "And how exactly are you gonna do that?"
    Amber "И как ты собираешься это сделать?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:695
translate spanish hwb_s05_153036ce:

    # Mariah "Come back to my base, {w=0.4}full of highly trained, elite treasure hunters. {w=0.7}Then I'll show you."
    Mariah "Вернемся на мою базу, {w=0.4} полную тренированных, элитных охотников за сокровищами. {w=0.7}Там я тебе покажу."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:700
translate spanish hwb_s05_80597f2d:

    # Amber "Elite what now?"
    Amber "Тренированных кого?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:705
translate spanish hwb_s05_d944507c:

    # Mariah "Highly trained, {w=0.5}elite {w=0.55}treasure hunters."
    Mariah "Тренированных, {w=0.5}элитных {w=0.55}охотников за сокровищами."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:710
translate spanish hwb_s05_ff93d212:

    # Amber "{cps=15}Riiiiiiiight.{/cps}"
    Amber "{cps=15}Окееееей.{/cps}"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:716
translate spanish hwb_s05_00f96ab9:

    # Amber "Thanks, but no thanks. We’ll pass."
    Amber "Спасибо, конечно, но нет. Мы не пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:722
translate spanish hwb_s05_3e7d239f:

    # Marina "What? But why?"
    Marina "Что? Но почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:726
translate spanish hwb_s05_8157d7b4:

    # Amber "Well, because—"
    Amber "Потому, что—"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:734
translate spanish hwb_s05_38b363dd:

    # Marina "You said we needed a game plan, right?"
    Marina "Ты говорила, нам нужен план?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:736
translate spanish hwb_s05_02c80a29:

    # Marina "This is the best chance we have right now!"
    Marina "Сейчас у нас есть отличная возможность!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:740
translate spanish hwb_s05_12aa5896:

    # "A terrifying amount of determination emanates from her as she forces an unwavering stare on me."
    "Una cantidad aterradora de determinación emana de ella mientras me clava una mirada inquebrantable."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:744
translate spanish hwb_s05_1c6a12ae:

    # "Her gaze intensifies. I look down at my dusty shoes and finally give in."
    "Su mirada se intensifica. Bajo la vista hacia mis zapatos polvorientos y finalmente cedo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:749
translate spanish hwb_s05_cd11591d:

    # Amber "Geez, if it’ll make you that happy, I’ll do it."
    Amber "Блин, если это сделает тебя счастливой, то пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:753
translate spanish hwb_s05_e790968e:

    # Marina "Yay!"
    Marina "Ура!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:755
translate spanish hwb_s05_bdc9ef2d:

    # "She’s really damned determined, I’ll give her that much. I’m not sure I could have said no."
    "Está realmente empecinada, eso se lo concedo. No estoy segura de haber podido decir que no."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:759
translate spanish hwb_s05_588aaab0:

    # Amber "But this better be legit, ya hear?"
    Amber "Только ничего противозаконного, слышь?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:765
translate spanish hwb_s05_bad90f4e:

    # "I point to Mariah."
    "Señalo a Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:767
translate spanish hwb_s05_27814f63:

    # Amber "I’m not in the mood to be jerked around today."
    Amber "Сегодня я не в настроении для подобных афер."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:771
translate spanish hwb_s05_2392e551:

    # Mariah "Yeah, yeah. I’ll keep my word."
    Mariah "Да, да. Я сдержу свое слово."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:777
translate spanish hwb_s05_080e8b0d:

    # "Man" "{size=+10}HEY STOP IT!{/size}" with hpunch
    Man "{size=+10}ПРЕКРАТИТЕ ЭТО НЕМЕДЛЕННО!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:779
translate spanish hwb_s05_7962e628:

    # "We look back to the crowd. The guardrails have toppled over, and the crowd surge toward the man."
    "Volvemos a mirar a la multitud. Las barandillas se han derrumbado y la gente se abalanza hacia el hombre."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:781
translate spanish hwb_s05_9ab9fe3b:

    # "Man" "I’M WARNING YOU! STAY BACK! I HAVE A MEGAPHONE!"
    Man "Я ВАС ПРЕДУПРЕЖДАЮ! ОТОЙДИТЕ! У МЕНЯ ЕСТЬ МЕГАФОН!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:785
translate spanish hwb_s05_70e71a72:

    # "The crowd circles in around the chair and topples it over, the man crashing down with it."
    "La multitud rodea la silla y la vuelca, y el hombre cae junto con ella."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:789
translate spanish hwb_s05_67572e90:

    # Mariah "We should probably scram."
    Mariah "Нам пора сматываться."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:793
translate spanish hwb_s05_edc90061:

    # Amber "Way ahead of you."
    Amber "Веди."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:801
translate spanish hwb_s05_6fbe5d21:

    # "Sleek and lavish, Mariah’s motorhome is like a mansion on wheels. Its chromy, black paint is so fresh that you can practically smell the primer."
    "Elegante y lujosa, la casa rodante de Mariah es como una mansión sobre ruedas. Su pintura negra y cromada es tan nueva que casi se huele la imprimación."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:803
translate spanish hwb_s05_0975288b:

    # Mariah "Here we are. Base sweet base."
    Mariah "Мы пришли. Дом, милый дом."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:805
translate spanish hwb_s05_76b40e17:

    # "She throws the door open."
    "Abre la puerta de golpe."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:807
translate spanish hwb_s05_be59101f:

    # Mariah "Joe! Tess! Buck up, we have guests."
    Mariah "Джо! Тесс! Встряхнитесь, у нас гости."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:809
translate spanish hwb_s05_78f18413:

    # "Marina and I shoot each other an unsure glance, then enter the motorhome."
    "Marina y yo nos lanzamos una mirada de incertidumbre, luego entramos a la casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:867
translate spanish hwb_s05_9ade7ae4:

    # "{color=#FF9201}???{/color}" "Oh hey, did you finally manage to make some friends?"
    BandanaGuy "О, привет, ты наконец-то завела друзей?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:872
translate spanish hwb_s05_ed11148c:

    # Mariah "Blow it out your ass, slacker."
    Mariah "Иди в задницу, бездельник."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:874
translate spanish hwb_s05_b0334f01:

    # "It’s just as big and expansive on the inside, making my RV look like a toilet in comparison."
    "Es igual de grande y espacioso por dentro, lo que hace que mi RV parezca un inodoro en comparación."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:876
translate spanish hwb_s05_2a3e160e:

    # "It’s definitely a luxury class, unlike my Class C."
    "Definitivamente es de clase de lujo, a diferencia de mi Clase C."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:878
translate spanish hwb_s05_ed828245:

    # "Or at least, it would be a luxury motorhome if not for the seemingly random decor."
    "O al menos, lo sería si no fuera por la decoración aparentemente aleatoria."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:880
translate spanish hwb_s05_65050856:

    # "The wall is littered with posters of ska bands—the worst genre of music. Even weirder are the license plates scattered everywhere. Some in boxes, some on the table, and some strung together like a windchime."
    "La pared está llena de pósters de bandas de ska, el peor género musical. Aún más extrañas son las placas de matrícula esparcidas por todas partes. Algunas en cajas, otras en la mesa, y otras colgadas como un móvil de viento."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:882
translate spanish hwb_s05_4f52a798:

    # "A beanbag in the corner and bottles of empty beer and liquor cast off on the ground, the place looks more like fratpad than a ‘base.’"
    "Un puf en la esquina y botellas vacías de cerveza y licor tiradas en el suelo, el lugar parece más una guarida de fraternidad que una \"base\"."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:884
translate spanish hwb_s05_e78561b7:

    # "An impression further aided by the guy sprawled out on the couch, his head wrapped in a bandanna like Mariah’s."
    "Una impresión reforzada por el tipo tirado en el sofá, con la cabeza envuelta en un pañuelo como el de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:890
translate spanish hwb_s05_8268237b:

    # BandanaGuy "Someone’s feisty today. No luck with the treasure, I take it."
    BandanaGuy "Кто-то сегодня злой. Неудача с сокровищем, как я понимаю."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:892
translate spanish hwb_s05_3ef686d7:

    # Mariah "Yeah, no thanks to you."
    Mariah "Ага, благодаря тебе."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:894
translate spanish hwb_s05_5793b50e:

    # BandanaGuy "Hey now, me and Tess were holding down the fort. That’s a very important job."
    BandanaGuy "Эй, мы с Тесс поддерживаем порядок на борту. Это очень важная задача."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:896
translate spanish hwb_s05_df8a98d1:

    # "He gestures at the cot above him. A hollow space under some cabinets, it looks like a row of cupboards used to be there and were stripped out to make room for it. Lying on top of it is a little girl facing the other direction, fiddling with something I can’t make out."
    "Señala el catre que tiene encima. Un espacio hueco debajo de unos armarios, parece que antes había una fila de alacenas que fueron retiradas para hacerle espacio. Acostada sobre él hay una niña pequeña mirando hacia el otro lado, manipulando algo que no logro distinguir."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:898
translate spanish hwb_s05_04a6bd98:

    # "She’s wearing another identical bandana."
    "Lleva otro pañuelo idéntico."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:900
translate spanish hwb_s05_ee667097:

    # BandanaGuy "Isn’t that right, Tess?"
    BandanaGuy "Не так ли Тесс?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:915
translate spanish hwb_s05_3347e5f8:

    # Tess "..."
    Tess "..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:920
translate spanish hwb_s05_be2decd2:

    # "‘Tess’ gives a barely existent nod, and continues tinkering."
    "\"Tess\" asiente casi imperceptiblemente y sigue manipulando."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:926
translate spanish hwb_s05_dcd4a1d9:

    # BandanaGuy "See? What did I tell you?"
    BandanaGuy "Видишь? Что я тебе говорил?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:930
translate spanish hwb_s05_9bb362a8:

    # Mariah "Has she been like that the entire time?"
    Mariah "Неужели она так сидела все время?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:934
translate spanish hwb_s05_50c206a9:

    # BandanaGuy "Yep. She hasn’t moved since you left this morning. It’s kind of sad."
    BandanaGuy "Ага. Она не сдвинулась с места, пока тебя не было. Это печально."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:938
translate spanish hwb_s05_1522f4ff:

    # Mariah "Please, don't think I haven't noticed you were on that couch when I left."
    Mariah "Умоляю, думаешь я не заметила, что ты как лежал на диване, так и лежишь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:942
translate spanish hwb_s05_6c68f7e3:

    # BandanaGuy "Guilty as charged."
    BandanaGuy "Виновен по всем статьям."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:955
translate spanish hwb_s05_a470c9b6:

    # "I clear my throat, reminding them of our presence."
    "Me aclaro la garganta, recordándoles nuestra presencia."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:959
translate spanish hwb_s05_90c8ca16:

    # Mariah "Oh, right."
    Mariah "Ох, верно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:963
translate spanish hwb_s05_113c9a6e:

    # Mariah "This is my team."
    Mariah "Это моя команда."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:965
translate spanish hwb_s05_649a619d:

    # Mariah "The lug who’s become one with the couch is Joseph, and the squirt is my kid sister, Tess."
    Mariah "Олух на диване - Джозеф, соплячка - моя младшая сестра Тесс."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:967
translate spanish hwb_s05_df6d0ba0:

    # Mariah "Joe. Tess. This is Alyssa and Malena."
    Mariah "Джо. Тесс. Это Алиса и Малена."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:971
translate spanish hwb_s05_6c921b89:

    # Amber "Amber and Marina."
    Amber "Эмбер и Марина."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:975
translate spanish hwb_s05_f0438e23:

    # Mariah "Whatever."
    Mariah "Не важно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:977
translate spanish hwb_s05_2d68c604:

    # Mariah "They’re looking for the treasure, too."
    Mariah "Они тоже ищут сокровище."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:983
translate spanish hwb_s05_8e037691:

    # Joseph "Hey there, ladies."
    Joseph "Привет, дамы."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:985
translate spanish hwb_s05_e5cd2315:

    # "I can only hope the highly trained, elite team are hidden in the bathroom."
    "Solo puedo esperar que el equipo altamente entrenado y de élite esté escondido en el baño."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:993
translate spanish hwb_s05_ae68d989:

    # Marina "Hey! I’m Marina! It’s really nice to meet you!"
    Marina "Привет! Я Марина! Рада с вами познакомиться!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:995
translate spanish hwb_s05_411e72a7:

    # "Marina jumps in front of me, taking hold of the conversation by its throat."
    "Marina se pone frente a mí, tomando el control de la conversación por el cuello."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1000
translate spanish hwb_s05_fe15de9f:

    # Marina "The other girl is Amber. Say hi, Amber!"
    Marina "Вторая девчонка — Эмбер. Скажи привет, Эмбер!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1005
translate spanish hwb_s05_26ae23b0:

    # Amber "Hi."
    Amber "Привет."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1007
translate spanish hwb_s05_e6a47e4e:

    # Marina "Don’t mind her. She’s just grumpy."
    Marina "Не берите в голову. Она просто ворчунья."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1011
translate spanish hwb_s05_bb2f62d2:

    # Amber "I’m not grumpy!"
    Amber "Я не ворчунья!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1015
translate spanish hwb_s05_88be18b0:

    # Joseph "You sound pretty grumpy to me."
    Joseph "Как по мне, ты довольно ворчливая."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1019
translate spanish hwb_s05_0ef6b1b9:

    # "I groan and start muttering nonsense under my breath."
    "Gimo y empiezo a murmurar tonterías en voz baja."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1021
translate spanish hwb_s05_fdfc4dca:

    # "Didn’t think being a realist would make me ‘grumpy.’"
    "No pensé que ser realista me haría parecer \"gruñona\"."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1025
translate spanish hwb_s05_e44a8630:

    # Marina "She doesn’t think the treasure exists."
    Marina "Она не верит в существование сокровища."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1029
translate spanish hwb_s05_71760c23:

    # Joseph "Uh-oh. Mariah, we’ve got a non-believer in our midst."
    Joseph "Хо-хо. Мария, в наших рядах скептик."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1031
translate spanish hwb_s05_2a90ee70:

    # "Why do they keep saying that?"
    "¿Por qué siguen diciendo eso?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1035
translate spanish hwb_s05_424f5843:

    # Mariah "Why do you think I brought her here?"
    Mariah "А почему, ты думаешь, я привела ее сюда?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1039
translate spanish hwb_s05_91dc8f08:

    # Amber "If you think you’ll be able to convince me that this treasure is real, then fine, but you have another thing coming."
    Amber "Если ты убедишь меня в том, что сокровище реально, тогда ладно, но ты глубоко заблуждаешься."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1043
translate spanish hwb_s05_27ffe153:

    # Marina "C’mon, where’s your sense of adventure?"
    Marina "Да ладно, где твой дух приключений?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1047
translate spanish hwb_s05_8fed2daa:

    # Amber "Back in my motorhome. We can take you and your sense of adventure back to Carlsbad if you want."
    Amber "Остался в трейлере. Мы можем вернуть тебя и твой дух приключений обратно в Карлсбад, если хочешь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1051
translate spanish hwb_s05_2761e137:

    # Marina "N-No thanks."
    Marina "Н-нет, спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1055
translate spanish hwb_s05_2f0c630a:

    # Joseph "Carlsbad? California?"
    Joseph "Карлсбад? Калифорния?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1059
translate spanish hwb_s05_a310ddec:

    # Amber "New Mexico."
    Amber "Нью-Мексико."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1066
translate spanish hwb_s05_049a7505:

    # "Rolling her eyes, Mariah walks over to a drawer. From inside, she pulls out something wrapped in cloth and brings it over to me."
    "Rodando los ojos, Mariah camina hacia un cajón. De adentro, saca algo envuelto en un trapo y lo trae hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1071
translate spanish hwb_s05_08220056:

    # Mariah "Go ahead. Take a peek."
    Mariah "Давай. Взгляни."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1073
translate spanish hwb_s05_3c958c43:

    # "Her smirk reappears, curling across her face as if this were a game and there’s no way she could lose. Hesitant, I bring my hand to the rag and unwrap it."
    "Su sonrisa burlona reaparece, curvándose en su rostro como si esto fuera un juego y no hubiera forma de que perdiera. Con dudas, llevo mi mano al trapo y lo desenvuelvo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1079
translate spanish hwb_s05_539936a6:

    # Amber "What? No way. Is this…"
    Amber "Что? Исключено. Это же..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1081
translate spanish hwb_s05_730e9dea:

    # Mariah "That’s right."
    Mariah "Именно."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1083
translate spanish hwb_s05_629dabb8:

    # "Lying swaddled in the cloth is a yellow nugget."
    "Acostado y envuelto en el trapo hay un pepita amarilla."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1085
translate spanish hwb_s05_55ddb4d3:

    # "I give it a squeeze. It's soft; definitely not a piece of pyrite."
    "Le doy un apretón. Es suave; definitivamente no es un trozo de pirita."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1089
translate spanish hwb_s05_cf4c9abe:

    # Marina "It’s… gold!"
    Marina "Это же... золото!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1091
translate spanish hwb_s05_5da75863:

    # Amber "But how?"
    Amber "Но как?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1093
translate spanish hwb_s05_a39b219d:

    # Mariah "You know the miner, who hid the treasure? That’s Joseph’s great great uncle."
    Mariah "Вы слышали о старателе, который спрятал сокровище? Он был пра-пра-дядей Джозефа."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1097
translate spanish hwb_s05_731ad956:

    # Amber "Y-You’re lying."
    Amber "В-врешь."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1101
translate spanish hwb_s05_34d54b70:

    # Joseph "I can testify for that. It’s true."
    Joseph "Я могу подтвердить. Это правда."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1107
translate spanish hwb_s05_ec5b730c:

    # Mariah "This thing is a family heirloom!"
    Mariah "Эта вещь - фамильная реликвия!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1110
translate spanish hwb_s05_40a304e5:

    # Joseph "More like it was lying forgotten in my basement until we stumbled across it as kids."
    Joseph "Точнее, он валялся забытым в подвале, пока мы не наткнулись на него еще в детстве."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1112
translate spanish hwb_s05_9f38bc7c:

    # Mariah "After that, I heard great tales of the miner and his hidden treasure!"
    Mariah "И потом я слышала много рассказов о старателе и его золотом сокровище!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1114
translate spanish hwb_s05_82f9958c:

    # Joseph "She went to the library and found old newspaper clippings making fun of him."
    Joseph "Она нашла старую газетную вырезку, высмеивающую его."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1116
translate spanish hwb_s05_37d13f15:

    # Mariah "Then, I made it my life’s goal to find his treasure!"
    Mariah "И тогда я решила посвятить жизнь поискам его сокровища!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1118
translate spanish hwb_s05_170266b9:

    # Joseph "She’s been obsessed with it ever since. {w=1.0}Help."
    Joseph "С тех самых пор она помешалась. {w=1.0}Помогите."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1122
translate spanish hwb_s05_ddbbeb26:

    # Amber "That’s a load. I saw you at the store the yesterday. If you knew so much about the treasure, then why did you have to buy one of those journals?"
    Amber "Чушь. Я видела тебя в магазине вчера. Если ты так много знаешь о сокровище, то зачем купила один из этих дневников?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1124
translate spanish hwb_s05_7ea1aa29:

    # Joseph "Another side of my family probably got the journal after he kicked it. We didn’t hear about it until everyone else did."
    Joseph "Другая часть моей семейки скорее всего прикарманила дневник, когда старикан отдал концы. Мы ни о чем не знали, пока все вокруг не пронюхали."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1128
translate spanish hwb_s05_3bbddb01:

    # Amber "This doesn’t prove anything!"
    Amber "Это ничего не подтверждает!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1132
translate spanish hwb_s05_04a98bfa:

    # "Mariah shoots me a scowl, similar to the look she gave to the clerk yesterday."
    "Mariah me lanza un ceño fruncido, parecido a la mirada que le dio al dependiente ayer."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1134
translate spanish hwb_s05_020ba331:

    # Mariah "What are you trying to say?"
    Mariah "Что ты хочешь сказать?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1136
translate spanish hwb_s05_a45f690b:

    # Tess "Sis."
    Tess "Сестренка."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1141
translate spanish hwb_s05_79a8e883:

    # "Tess finally moves, hopping down from her cot, another license plate windchime in her hand, the plates clanking together as she runs over to Mariah."
    "Tess finalmente se mueve, saltando de su catre, otro móvil de placas de matrícula en su mano, las placas chocando entre sí mientras corre hacia Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1143
translate spanish hwb_s05_37de5203:

    # Tess "Sis, I finished it."
    Tess "Сестренка, я закончила."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1145
translate spanish hwb_s05_af65d9de:

    # "She says this without a hint of emotion, her eyes in a constant half-open state."
    "Dice esto sin una pizca de emoción, sus ojos en un constante estado semicerrado."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1151
translate spanish hwb_s05_682efa8a:

    # "It’s kind of unsettling."
    "Es un poco inquietante."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1155
translate spanish hwb_s05_99c268c8:

    # Joseph "How many is that now? Forty-four?"
    Joseph "Какая это? Сорок четвертая?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1159
translate spanish hwb_s05_bda1cc2d:

    # Tess "Forty-five."
    Tess "Сорок пятая."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1168
translate spanish hwb_s05_c3628c17:

    # "Marina bends down to Tess’ level and greets her."
    "Marina se agacha al nivel de Tess y la saluda."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1170
translate spanish hwb_s05_eb994535:

    # Marina "Oh, are you collecting license plates?"
    Marina "Оо, ты коллекционируешь номерные знаки?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1176
translate spanish hwb_s05_67071f8d:

    # Tess "Uh-huh. I only have five more until I have all fifty states."
    Tess "Угу. Мне нужно еще пять, чтобы собрать пятьдесят штатов."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1178
translate spanish hwb_s05_37a82155:

    # Marina "And what state do you have there?"
    Marina "И что за штат у тебя здесь?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1180
translate spanish hwb_s05_06735c1c:

    # Tess "New Mexico."
    Tess "Нью-Мексико."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1182
translate spanish hwb_s05_69148818:

    # "Her voice and expression don't change, still as dry as the desert air."
    "Su voz y expresión no cambian, aún tan secas como el aire del desierto."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1191
translate spanish hwb_s05_33ced028:

    # "Mariah scoffs."
    "Mariah resopla."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1193
translate spanish hwb_s05_40d6c788:

    # Mariah "At least yesterday wasn’t a complete waste of time. That junker was a piece of crap."
    Mariah "По крайней мере, вчера время было потрачено не впустую. Та рухлядь была полным дерьмом."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1198
translate spanish hwb_s05_884dcff6:

    # "Wait a second."
    "Espera un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1200
translate spanish hwb_s05_d9ef78f9:

    # Mariah "All the parts were rustier than my ass. Even the scrap metal wasn’t worth it."
    Mariah "Все части были ржавее, чем моя задница. Даже на металлолом не сойдут."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1204
translate spanish hwb_s05_a1abf868:

    # Joseph "Just be thankful we found it. We’d be busted if I hadn’t salvaged the good bits. Besides, that money is going to keep us from starving."
    Joseph "Будь благодарна за то что мы нашли ее. Мы бы обанкротились, если бы я не распродал хорошие части. Кроме того, эти деньги не дадут нам умереть с голоду."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1206
translate spanish hwb_s05_4445e9ac:

    # "I look at Marina, but she doesn't seem to have put it together."
    "Miro a Marina, pero ella no parece haberlo entendido."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1210
translate spanish hwb_s05_b86b1f71:

    # Amber "Uh, about that car you found. That wasn’t outside Roswell, was it?"
    Amber "Амм, по поводу найденной вами машины. Вы ведь нашли ее у Розуэлла, не так ли?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1214
translate spanish hwb_s05_1937cd21:

    # "Marina's eyes go wide, realisation finally penetrating her skull."
    "Los ojos de Marina se abren de par en par, la comprensión finalmente penetrando su cráneo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1218
translate spanish hwb_s05_bf4d937e:

    # Mariah "Yeah, not too far from the store. What do you care?"
    Mariah "Да, недалеко от магазина. Вам-то какая разница?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1222
translate spanish hwb_s05_52b0d61b:

    # "I can feel my blood begin to boil. Marina can feel it too."
    "Siento que mi sangre empieza a hervir. Marina también lo siente."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1224
translate spanish hwb_s05_828df7c1:

    # Marina "Amber…"
    Marina "Эмбер..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1226
translate spanish hwb_s05_d2edb9d7:

    # "Every part of me is shaking. I struggle to spit out the words."
    "Cada parte de mí está temblando. Lucho por escupir las palabras."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1228
translate spanish hwb_s05_ea29609e:

    # Amber "Her car was stolen outside of Roswell yesterday."
    Amber "Ее машину угнали за Розуэллом вчера."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1232
translate spanish hwb_s05_0b3f2c38:

    # Amber "It was out of gas, so we went to get some."
    Amber "В ней кончился бензин и мы поехали за ним."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1237
translate spanish hwb_s05_cccdba6e:

    # "Joseph is the next to realize it, followed by Tess."
    "Joseph es el siguiente en darse cuenta, seguido por Tess."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1239
translate spanish hwb_s05_b0e154e2:

    # Joseph "Oh crap."
    Joseph "Вот дерьмо."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1241
translate spanish hwb_s05_6847a64b:

    # Mariah "So?"
    Mariah "И?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1243
translate spanish hwb_s05_4b180757:

    # "I can’t hold it in anymore. Sorry, Marina."
    "Ya no puedo contenerlo más. Lo siento, Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1247
translate spanish hwb_s05_0279afc9:

    # Amber "{cps=4}So...{/cps} {size=+10}YOU STOLE HER CAR AND DISMANTLED IT!{/size}" with hpunch
    Amber "{cps=4}Иии...{/cps} {size=+10}ВЫ УКРАЛИ И ДЕМОНТИРОВАЛИ ЕЕ МАШИНУ!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1253
translate spanish hwb_s05_c36940d8:

    # "Joseph jumps off the couch and apologetically bows repeatedly, all in one swift motion. Each bow makes me a little bit angrier."
    "Joseph salta del sofá y se inclina repetidamente en señal de disculpa, todo en un movimiento rápido. Cada inclinación me enfurece un poco más."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1258
translate spanish hwb_s05_95ba91f6:

    # Tess "Joey said it was okay."
    Tess "Джоуи сказал, что все нормально."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1261
translate spanish hwb_s05_0ac29bce:

    # Joseph "I thought it was! Mariah gave the go ahead."
    Joseph "Я так думал! Мария дала добро."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1265
translate spanish hwb_s05_e4925936:

    # Amber "{i}You{/i} told them it was alright?!"
    Amber "{i}Ты{/i} сказала им, что все в порядке?!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1269
translate spanish hwb_s05_834112c5:

    # Mariah "Yeah, so? It’s your own fault for leaving it out there!"
    Mariah "Да, и что? Вы сами виноваты, что оставили ее там!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1274
translate spanish hwb_s05_6f17b886:

    # Amber "{i}How?{/i} How on earth is it our fault that it broke down?!"
    Amber "{i}В чем?{/i} Мы виноваты в том, что она сломалась?!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1277
translate spanish hwb_s05_9f12fdf4:

    # Mariah "You know…"
    Mariah "Ну знаешь..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1279
translate spanish hwb_s05_097ced09:

    # Mariah "Finder’s keeper’s."
    Mariah "Что с возу упало."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1282
translate spanish hwb_s05_9c8d8596:

    # Amber "{size=+10}IT’S A FREAKIN’ CAR!{/size}" with hpunch
    Amber "{size=+10}ЭТО ЧЕРТОВА МАШИНА!{/size}" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1289
translate spanish hwb_s05_0193e6fa:

    # Tess "Um…"
    Tess "Эмм..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1291
translate spanish hwb_s05_4d1e62dd:

    # "Tess tugs on my shirt."
    "Tess tira de mi camisa."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1295
translate spanish hwb_s05_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1299
translate spanish hwb_s05_d9c86fdd:

    # "I don’t mean to, but the word snaps out of my mouth. The tiny girl shrinks away."
    "No es mi intención, pero la palabra sale disparada de mi boca. La pequeña niña se encoge."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1303
translate spanish hwb_s05_cf5c9112:

    # "Alright Amber, just calm down. We can talk this out."
    "Está bien, Amber, solo cálmate. Podemos resolver esto hablando."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1307
translate spanish hwb_s05_40f8880c:

    # Tess "Here."
    Tess "Вот."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1309
translate spanish hwb_s05_93535582:

    # "She holds out the wind chime made of Marina’s license plate, her eyes cast downward."
    "Sostiene el carillón hecho con la placa de Marina, con la mirada hacia abajo."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1311
translate spanish hwb_s05_54a166c0:

    # Tess "You can have it."
    Tess "Можешь взять ее."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1315
translate spanish hwb_s05_2fb2a4a0:

    # "Never mind. Calming down isn’t gonna happen."
    "Olvídalo. Calmarse no va a pasar."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1324
translate spanish hwb_s05_855cb30d:

    # "A hand grasp my shoulder. I turn to Marina. She shakes her head and smiles."
    "Una mano agarra mi hombro. Me giro hacia Marina. Ella niega con la cabeza y sonríe."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1326
translate spanish hwb_s05_0f86c418:

    # Marina "Amber, it’s okay."
    Marina "Эмбер, все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1330
translate spanish hwb_s05_7441eaf8:

    # Amber "But—"
    Amber "Но—"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1334
translate spanish hwb_s05_29da5489:

    # Marina "Really. It’s fine."
    Marina "Правда. Все хорошо."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1340
translate spanish hwb_s05_112ac2bc:

    # "She bends back down to Tess and smiles reassuringly."
    "Se inclina de nuevo hacia Tess y le sonríe de manera tranquilizadora."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1342
translate spanish hwb_s05_26534b50:

    # Marina "You go ahead and keep it, sweetie."
    Marina "Можешь оставить ее себе, милая."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1349
translate spanish hwb_s05_ffbbaf57:

    # "The trio, Mariah included, are taken back by Marina’s saint-like reaction."
    "El trío, incluida Mariah, queda sorprendido por la reacción casi santurrona de Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1353
translate spanish hwb_s05_b8b6561d:

    # Marina "Don’t worry, guys. It’s fine."
    Marina "Не переживайте ребята. Все в порядке."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1360
translate spanish hwb_s05_6f9a02f7:

    # "Joseph breathes a sigh of relief."
    "Joseph exhala un suspiro de alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1362
translate spanish hwb_s05_9f976dae:

    # Joseph "Oh god, thank you so much."
    Joseph "Слава богу, огромное спасибо."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1364
translate spanish hwb_s05_8b11903d:

    # Joseph "We’re all really sorry about this. Right, Mariah?"
    Joseph "Нам всем ужасно жаль. Правда, Мария?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1368
translate spanish hwb_s05_8667baa6:

    # Mariah "Yeah, I guess…"
    Mariah "Да, я полагаю..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1378
translate spanish hwb_s05_0f9c0a49:

    # "About as fed up with this as I am, Joseph shoots her a glare and smacks her on the back of the head."
    "Tan harto como yo de esto, Joseph le lanza una mirada fulminante y le da una palmada en la nuca."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1383
translate spanish hwb_s05_991ed580:

    # Mariah "Ow! Alright, I’m sorry and stuff."
    Mariah "Оу! Да, я извиняюсь и все такое."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1387
translate spanish hwb_s05_8a3a4869:

    # Amber "Marina, are you sure? They destroyed your car."
    Amber "Марина, ты уверена? Они уничтожили твою машину."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1391
translate spanish hwb_s05_70fc7141:

    # Marina "Yeah, but it was pretty rundown anyway."
    Marina "Да, но она и так еле ездила."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1395
translate spanish hwb_s05_28452f91:

    # Amber "You’re unreal, you know that?"
    Amber "Ты ненормальная, знаешь?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1399
translate spanish hwb_s05_26458fac:

    # Amber "Anyway, we should head out now. We have a few things to take care of."
    Amber "В любом случае, нам пора. У нас есть еще есть дела, о которых стоит позаботиться."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1405
translate spanish hwb_s05_998d454a:

    # Marina "Thanks for showing us the gold! Now I’m sure the treasure is real."
    Marina "Спасибо, что показали нам золото! Теперь я уверена в том, что сокровище реально."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1407
translate spanish hwb_s05_304ad5a0:

    # Joseph "No problem, ladies."
    Joseph "Никаких проблем, дамы."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1409
translate spanish hwb_s05_1ed4a9aa:

    # Joseph "Again, really sorry for all the trouble. If there’s anything we can do for you, just give us a shout."
    Joseph "Еще раз, простите за все неудобства. Если мы можем сделать что-то для вас, только намекните."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1411
translate spanish hwb_s05_a9c1f36f:

    # Marina "Sure thing!"
    Marina "Конечно!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1419
translate spanish hwb_s05_74f55687:

    # "We head for the door, but Marina turns around before stepping outside."
    "Nos dirigimos a la puerta, pero Marina se da la vuelta antes de salir."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1425
translate spanish hwb_s05_566965a3:

    # Marina "By the way, was there a phone in the car?"
    Marina "Кстати, в машине был телефон?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1429
translate spanish hwb_s05_22f7765e:

    # Joseph "The pink Heisei?"
    Joseph "Розовый Хейсей?"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1433
translate spanish hwb_s05_e02a33c5:

    # Marina "Yeah! That’s the one!"
    Marina "Да! Это он!"

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1439
translate spanish hwb_s05_ff0aac2f:

    # Joseph "Ah…"
    Joseph "Ох..."

# game/script/hwb_s05.rpy:1445
translate spanish hwb_s05_e458216e:

    # Joseph "We kind of sold that too."
    Joseph "Его мы тоже продали."

